### Priority Recommendations

The **most impactful fix** would address findings 1.1-1.3 and 3.1 together: have `_validate_path` return the resolved `Path` object (or an error string), and have all three tools use the resolved path for actual file I/O. This is a single architectural change that closes 4 findings at once, including all HIGH-severity items.

The missing `edit_file` exception-handling test (3.2) is a straightforward addition.
