# Adversarial Code Review: Story 1.6 — Persistent Server & CLI Entry Point

**Files reviewed:**
- `src/main.py` (implementation)
- `tests/test_main.py` (tests)
- `src/agent/graph.py` (dependency — graph factory)
- `src/agent/state.py` (dependency — state schema)
